** Homepage slider - homepage partial **
- Draggable section
- Uses blocks
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %}Is the color set to transparent?{% endcomment %}
{% assign mobile_text_alpha = section.settings.mobile_text_color | color_extract: 'alpha' %}


